# QuinnBank Core
# Enterprise Java/Spring Boot git hygiene.
#
# Rules:
# - Commit source, migrations, docs, Gradle wrapper scripts, and wrapper jar.
# - Never commit secrets, private keys, local credentials, database dumps, logs,
#   generated reports, build outputs, or machine-specific IDE state.

HELP.md

### Gradle / Java build outputs ###
.gradle/
build/
out/
target/
bin/
classes/
generated/
annotation-processing/
*.class
*.jar
*.war
*.ear

!gradle/wrapper/gradle-wrapper.jar
!**/src/main/**/build/
!**/src/test/**/build/
!**/src/main/**/out/
!**/src/test/**/out/
!**/src/main/**/bin/
!**/src/test/**/bin/

